chat.msg: hey, estas listo?
Hi si estoy ready
cool! entonces, estoy empezando en un punto con una ramita a mi izquierda que lleva a una isla con un tigre
¿por dónde me dirijo?
sigue adelanta hacia otra ramita que es como un puente a otra isla. go straight
vale, cruce la ramita al otro lado para la isla con la mariposa
¿y ahora qué?
no perdon regresa a la isla con el tiguere y cruza la otra ramita que esta strAIGHT
genial, estoy de vuelta en la isla del tigre y voy hacia la ramita que está al frente
ahora estoy en una isla más grande con un loro en un árbol. ¿cuál es el próximo paso?
ahora sigue la ruta cruzando un elephante hasta que llegues a unas rocas y la uses para cruzar a otra islita con una rana
hecho, crucé por el elefante y usé las rocas para llegar a la islita con la rana
¿dónde voy ahora?
ahora sigue adelanta a una curba, y cruza un alligator y unas mas rocas
ok, he pasado al cocodrilo y las rocas adicionales
pasa la jirafa y cruza otra ramia hasta que llegues a una culebra, la cruzas y llegaras al tesoro
he pasado por la jirafa, la ramita, la serpiente y
¡Encontró el tesoro! *terminado* ¿jugamos otra partida?
hola, q tal? ready to go?
si im ready
cool! to start, take a few steps west, just under that wooden bench and cross the trail
you see that flower stand, right?
i do see the flower stand. should i pass it?
nope, actually just pull a u-turn to the left, away from that stand
cross the trail again heading back towards our little white dog starting point
ok im at the white dog now what
great job! now, cross over that branch to the south, and keep heading down until you see another white dog by a picnic
ok im at the second white do
amazing! now scoot on over that picnic mat, give a touch to those berries, and continue heading west
i did that now im at a branch
perfect! cross that branch, heading north this time
ok i crossed
super! now sneak around the right side of that green bush near you
don't touch it! continue till you reach the flower stand
great im at the flower stand
awesome! now go left, pass under that stand, and head towards the big bridge
you will see two people biking there
should i cross the bridge?
no need for that! just pass by it, and keep heading west
ok i went under the stand and passed the bridge
you're doing amazing! just past the bridge, you'll spot two elderly people reading newspapers
enjoy the sights!
should i head towards them?
yeah! but make a quick turn to the south, between ol' folks and that wooden branch
go till you reach a green bush
hi there! que comience el juego!!
hola ves el mapa?
¡hola! sí, veo el mapa
estoy en la tienda del norte. ¿hacia dónde debo ir?
vas a cruzar unas rocas straight ahead until you reach a path and pass a telescope
vale, voy adelante hasta llegar al camino
he visto el telescopio azul. ¿izquierda o derecha ahora?
ahora vas hacia la izquierda y sigue adelanta hasta llegar a un caro azul
entendido, voy a la izquierda hasta el coche azul
¿y después qué?
despues te devuelves y vas en la grama past a mushroom and camp fire
ok, volveré y pasaré por un hongo y el fuego de campamento
¿siguen más instrucciones?
sigue hasta pasar un perro despues sigue en la grama para riba hasta la tent
¡entendido! pasaré el perro y seguiré subiendo hasta la tienda
tent?
oh sorry for the confusion
Where should I go after passing the dog?
continue north towards the tent and that should be the end
brilliant! I'm in the store now
Was this the end?
yes
awesome! we did it! *finished*
hey, estas listo?
hi im ready
awesome! go southwest under the first palm tree. hook right at the second tree, then take a sharp left before the third
walk southwards now. how's that going?
ok i reached the sand and a dog
great! that's our brown puppy
move to its left, then veer a bit left and right to the south. watch out not to step on his tail!
ok i did that
perfect! now, you should see some rocks up ahead
you’re gonna pass right between a big rock on your left and a small one on your right. can you see it?
yes i passed through them
nice work! you are right on track
now, you're gonna get your feet wet. walk into the water ahead
ok i see a crab
exactly, the big red fella! take a right at the crab, and follow the rock
keep going west in the water
ok im passing the big rock
great job, mate! keep going until you see a third, medium-sized rock
im at the medium size rock now where to?
don't get scared but you’ll see a shark in the water
just make a sharp right. you're doing awesome!
back towards the shore/
yes, headed back to dry land now
pass between the medium rock and a colorful ball. got it?
yup i passed both now what
good job! continue north now and veer slightly left
ok im at the sand now
awesome! now, do you see a rad red tent and a big speaker?
yes
thread between them, heading to the north-west
almost there, pal!
ok i am between them and past that a little
sweet! now, make a arc around the tent and then head south
you've got this!
ok did that
good job! now look for the shore but don’t hit the water yet!
ok got it now what
see that epic red kayak? turn right and go under it
how are you holding up?
great im passed under it
awesome sauce! now, turn around
like a full 90 degrees to the right, heading north along the kayak
ok thats done
fantastic! you should see a cute little green bush now, right?
yes i see it
nailed it! you've reached our end point
thanks for playing along, partner! how was the trek?
great thanks to your clear instructions
that's great to hear! thanks for being such a good sport
looking forward to our next map challenge!
